  "coOpRequirements": "<h3>Co-op requirements</h3> <p>Refer to the <a href=\"#/experiences/B1emM4RiN\">Physics and Astronomy Co-operative Education Program</a> and the <a href=\"#/experiences/Bkc5P4qs4\">Earth and Ocean Sciences Co-operative Education Program</a>.</p>",
