  "dateStart": "2025-09-02",
  "description": "<p>This single degree program is composed of a selected combination of courses from the the <a href=\"#/experiences/SkgBpgRoE\">Department of Physics and Astronomy</a> and the <a href=\"#/experiences/rJeiHV5iV\">School of Earth and Ocean Sciences</a>. Students complete this program in the <a href=\"#/experiences/rJwWOW5oN\">Faculty of Science</a> and must consult the <a href=\"#/experiences/BylJ9-cs4\">Faculty Requirements</a>.</p> <p>Students should also refer to the <a href=\"#/experiences/S1Mc0lAjE\">Physics and Astronomy Requirements</a> and the <a href=\"#/experiences/Bygp8EcjV\">Earth and Ocean Sciences Requirements</a>.</p>",
